&lt;li&gt;Enjoy engaging others, working collaboratively, and developing strong working relationships at all levels of management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passionate about leading strategic payments conversations, presenting business reviews, and coordinating high level technical discussions&lt;/li&gt;
