&lt;li&gt;Commercial acumen: Drive commercial discussions for joint accounts, while striving to meet strategic and financial targets.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project management: Prioritize and manage short and long term projects with varying timelines across multiple accounts, leveraging internal support teams where relevant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Affinity: Analytical and data-driven thinker who feels comfortable with spreadsheet analysis and technical discussions about the nuances of payments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Feedback: Serve as a feedback loop for your customers internally.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
